title: Poppins:: Book One
description: I was born by accident. I'm dying by chance. That is beyond my control. What is within my control is how I choose to live each and every day that I breathe.What I choose to do with my time as Poppins is to write, to live, to bring my experiences and knowledge to as many people as possible. That will not always be the case. I guess that's why I'm telling you this.
author: Karen Daly
